data.description: Welcome to this charming 2 bed 2 bath home in the heart of Guntersville! It has a large bonus room that could be used as a third bedroom, with a walk in closet just across the hall! The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring granite countertops and stainless steel gas appliances. All appliances remain with the home. Situated on almost 1.2 acres, you can enjoy the outdoors from the comfort of your screened in porch. There is an additional air- conditioned detached garage and 2 sheds located on the property, perfect for all of your spring projects! Located just minutes from beautiful Lake Guntersville, this home combines modern comforts with the tranquility of country living!
